Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.83,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Certifique-se de deixá-los vivos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.92,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Como se nada tivesse acontecido
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:52.05,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Sinta seus lábios prestes a fechar e diga a ele!
