Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:39.34,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Tada kono mama de itai dake
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:43.63,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Yusaburanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:46.80,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H4A2EFB&\blur3}Na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:55.94,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Daremo kuzusenai kizukiageta barikeedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:23:08.95,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Kataku tozashiteta hazu datta no ni doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:22.71,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}Do you hear weary heart’s S.O.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:22:04.84,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}Foi algo agradável e doce... até que ganhei juízo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:13.35,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HFFAE04&\blur3}Sempre foi algo cruel, escuro e doloroso
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:17.98,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}Toda vez que eu me aproximo... toda vez que eu brilho
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:22.03,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HACD837&\blur3}meu peito começa a acelerar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:25.99,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}Estou feliz, mas dói
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:30.37,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HDB2594&\blur3}De agora em diante, eu não deveria me forçar
